snippet.description:

snippet.title: De De Pyaar De 2 - Official Trailer | Ajay Devgn, R. Madhavan, Rakul Preet, Meezaan Jafri | 14th Nov
snippet.description:
In De De Pyaar De 2, love faces its toughest test yet as Ashish visits Ayesha’s family home!
Will the age-gap romance win hearts or stir things up? With heart, humour and a whole lot of family madness, this Pyaar vs Parivaar clash promises a relatable, riotous ride for every kind of audience.

De De Pyaar De 2 is directed by Anshul Sharma, produced by T-Series’ Bhushan Kumar & Krishan Kumar, and Luv Films’ Luv Ranjan & Ankur Garg. The film is set to release in cinemas on 14th November 2025.

#DeDePyaarDe2 #AjayDevgn #RMadhavan

Gulshan Kumar & T-Series Present 
A Luv Films Production

De De Pyaar De 2

Directed By: Anshul Sharma
Written By: Tarun Jain & Luv Ranjan
Produced By: Bhushan Kumar, Krishan Kumar
Produced by: Luv Ranjan & Ankur Garg

Story: Luv Ranjan
Director of Photography: Sudhir K. Chaudhary 
Music: Hitesh Sonik
Film Editor: Chetan M. Solanki 
Production Designer: Sumit Basu, Manini Mishra

Sound: Dhiman Karmakar
Casting Director: Vicky Sidana 
Executive Producer: Richard De Varda

snippet.title: Dhurandhar - Title Track | Ranveer Singh, Shashwat Sachdev, Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas,Aditya Dhar
snippet.description:
It’s here. It’s fierce.
The wait is over — the Dhurandhar Title Track (Jogi) is finally here!
Packed with fierce beats, bold voices, and unstoppable energy — this one’s pure fire. 🔥

Releasing on 5th December 2025

Credits: 
Jio Studios Presents
A B62 Studios Production

An Aditya Dhar Film
DHURANDHAR

Written, Directed and Produced by: Aditya Dhar
Produced by: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced by: Lokesh Dhar

Cast: Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna | R. Madhavan | Arjun Rampal | Sara Arjun

Audio Credits:
Original Song Name: Na De Dil Pardesi Nu (Jogi)
Song name: Dhurandhar - Title Track 
Music: Shashwat Sachdev, Charanjit Ahuja
Produced and Arranged: Shashwat Sachdev
Singers: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Sudhir Yaduvanshi, Shashwat Sachdev, Mohd. Sadiq, Ranjit Kaur
Lyrics: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Babu Singh Maan
Music Video: Jayesh Shikarkhane & Team
Mix and mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge 
Assistant engineers: Jazbaat, Sohamm, Suryansh
HanumanKind vocals mixed by Akash Shravan

हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

snippet.title: EMIWAY BANTAI - MERA NAAM HAI | OFFICIAL VIDEO | FTSTTS
snippet.description:
👉 (Lyrics are available below and in the captions as well)

Streaming Link : https://bfan.link/mera-naam-hai


Mera Naam Hai is a declaration of dominance, skill, and legacy!

Audio Credits
Song : Mera Naam Hai
Written & Performed by Emiway Bantai 
Producer : Tony James
Mix & Master : Mix with Vasudev
Background score - Memax

Video Credits
Production : Bantai Studio
Directed by : Emiway Bantai, Thrector 
Associate Director - Swaalina
Associate AD - Kala ka pratik
D.O.P : Thrector & Hardik Dilip Ranavshe
Edited by : Emiway Bantai & Thrector
Cc by : Thrector 
Vfx : Vbreak

Artwork by : Kala Ka Pratik
Costume designer : Bantai Studio
Artist Management : Bantai Studio
Hair & Make up : Rajeev Rajbhar
Line producer : Bantai Studio
Production Head : Sumit & Gaurav Bharti
Production Team : Hemanth, Guna, Pooja, Shubham, Abdul
Production Assistants : Mohan, Sagar Chitaare, Sagar Chaurasiya, Soyeb, Gunnjan
Light Gaffer : Rajesh Tripathi & Hardik Dilip Ranavshe
DIT : Bhavesh Thakur
BTS : Suraj Bara, Shashikant Varun, Jayesh Ambare

Merchandise here 👇🏻
https://www.bantai.in/product-categor...

Follow Emiway Bantai :- 

Instagram -  

 / emiwaybanta.  .
X - https://x.com/emiwaytweets?lang=en
Facebook -   

 / emiway37



(Lyrics)

(Verse)

Mera naam hai emiway bantai 
Flow aj bhi juna vidyalay 
Sab jante legend paida hua pachaanve
Pechante space de be bhai hai chaand pe 
Beef chaiye saand khada khule maidan mei 
Life dera test mei nai jara exam mei 
 Baggy pehnu maggi nahi khara mei ramen 
Meri hype is real par free palestine 

Buri nazar teri karle aankh pe parda tu 
Lagta ki fukta hai sasta garda tu 
Khauf bhi ha apne se khauf khata yaha pe toh 
Tere ilaake ko banadu mirzapur 
Flow inke out dated hai 
Ab likhta paper mei 
Patent hai mere pages toh 
Mujhe pay kare 
Playful hai wordplay pehle se 
Hum play kare 
Peth bharre mujhse leke beef 
Lekin pray karre 

Front cover pe nai aate bantai kya hai scene 
Ye paisa deke khabar mei 
Hum cover mei 
Bas khali karna janta mei magazine 
Book mei aur pen mera pistol hai 
Industry ka khel beta janega toh sab jhol
Hai band hole hai jabse mei aaya saare 
Rat fase pade 
Bane champ pehla rank leke khade 
Kare trap toh fir bag nai hum bank leke 
Khade chal 


(Hook)

Mera naam hai 
Bolna nai padta hai 
Ab mera kaam bolta hai 
Mera naam hai 
Naam aisa har koi hum ko 
Salaam thokta hai 
Mera naam hai 
Naam hai tabhi toh hum badnaam hai 
Chote 
Mera naam hai 
Haha malum hai na 

(Verse)

My bars got the barcode 
They’ll lead you to narcos 
Lines so dope got confused for cargos 
Look at these bitches calling me clown 
I’m pennywise with the pen drag kids itno dark holes 

Don’t ever f#ckin rap in english again, bi#ch.
Did your pu##y a## really trademark this language 
Bars soo savage i cut bandwidth for online 
Gangsters cyber damage 

I’m shredding the charts 
Heavy disaster for you su#kers
Steady with bars get ready for scars pen like a blade 
Tearing apart weapon in charge
Dropping these bombs 
Call me kim jong 
I’m lunatic armed 

You’re a frog in the pond 
I’m in the sea with the sharks 
Turning kings into pawns 
Selling combs to the bald 
Ek hi flow mei tu tatata
Lou#e ka baal karke bhi na 
Hota famous na liya hota ye naam 

(Hook) 

(Verse)

Bhai tera tufaan hai 
Aisa ye zubaan hai 
Summe sunta mujhe 
Bachkane tu fan hai 
Kyu panic hora be mujhjaisa 
Tu na hai 
Juna hai rhyme sceme logo ko
Lagara chuna hai hai 
Aae panwadi 
Mere bina scene pura suna hai 
Sunnata 
Yaha par hi banna tha 
Wyapari nai mujhe rapper hi 
Banna tha upar toh waise bhi 
Moksh hai ye baatein parlok se 
Expect kya karu par log se 
Kick karre day one se hustler hum 
Kok se 
Slow jara flow toh le force mei 

Opponent ko deta nai opportunity 
Brutally maru usse mei usually 
Har bari teri kyu jali 
Casually reppin globally 
Jab bola ye tu roo padi 
Mere bina tu nobody 
Dhua dia mei sober hi 
Ab aayi teri woh ghadi 
Bars du lage hathkadi 
Baaz nai aane wala mei 
Baaz bana hu upar hi 
Fast mei jab ye flow chali 
Saas na lu ye new delhi 
Pranaam kar hum too pak 
Iss naam se tu chalpadi

snippet.title: Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music
snippet.description:
Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music 

#payalkikhanak 
#पायल_की_खनक
#payal_ki_khanak
#पायल_की_खनक_से_जगेंगे_सजना
#payal_ki_khanak_se_jagege_sajna
#anilrawatkegane 
#anilrawat 
#anil_rawat 
#anilrawatsong
#अनिल_रावत_सोंग
payal ki khanak anil rawat song
पायल की खनक अनिल रावत सोंग
anil rawat viral song
अनिल रावत वायरल सोंग
payal ki khanak viral song



हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna

Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song Name - Bhugol Devra 
Hindi - भुगोल देवरा
Singer - Pramod Premi Yadav
Featuring - Priya Raghuvanshi 
Music - Abhishek Tiwari 
Lyrics - MP Yadav 
Director - Pawan Pathak & Raunak Raut
Assistant -Meenu Sharma & Vivek Mandal
Editor- Rohan 
Dop - Rahul Yadav

Lyrics:-

snippet.title: YUNG SAMMY feat. Seedhe Maut - MUDDA (Official Video) [prod. by Wamp]
snippet.description:
YUNG SAMMY feat. Seedhe Maut - MUDDA (Official Video) [prod. by Wamp]

Listen now: https://DESITRILL.lnk.to/YUNGSAMMY-MUDDA

YUNG SAMMY says “MUDDA” ain’t just a word, it’s an issue, a problem, a whole storm. When me and Seedhe Maut hit the studio, every line we wrote was about the scene, the hustle, the chaos. It’s called “MUDDA” ’cause when YUNG SAMMY and Seedhe Maut jump on a track, it’s not just music, it’s a warning. It’s trouble, it’s ruckus, it’s pressure on the whole game. We went all in, no filter, real talk straight from the hood. Turning struggles into flex, pain into power. “MUDDA” is an anthem, a rager, an energy you can’t ignore. This is heavyweight talk, facts only.”

Lyrics: 
ENCORE VERSE
Seedhe Maut Sammy hai, dikhta bas grey
Chai pe baithe hum London ya Noida
Lulli si shakal ka, bhidenge hum se
Hum rapper complete hai jaise Cu Boi ka
Hona jo waise bhi ho gaya
Tu toh pitega par bol kya karenge tere boy ka
Sona tha bandi ke chucho mein
Lekin vo aaj ki raat se khabar pe soyega
Kha kise kitno ki maa chodi x2
Aah ahh
Kamar se nikala ghoda aur bandi ko
Diya bana ghodi
Aah
Muh chodni karte hai baalak
Aur baalak aa karte hai muh chodi
Shakle dikhte hain news akhbaaron mein
Jaise main hoon Modi ooh ooh

Calm (1st Verse)
Kaha par hain rapper, ye dikhte nahi, gaayab hain
Dost inke SM pe flip ho rahi
Janwar hain baithe, teen rapper nahi
Papa hu ladko ka, chhaate mein chup ho rahe
Ye mic pe chilla rahe par inke ye jhaate se vocal nahi clip ho rahe, na na
Ye paisa, ye bitches, ye bud hai kamaaya
Bas music se, fatah bin filmon ke
Haan Greater Noida wala shit hai, saath hai Sammy jo
Ek bandi mujhko boli Calm se bajna hai, don’t say no
Main jau jaha paisa jaye, jab launde jaaye jaha booty go
If the truth be told, yaha dono ladke nuke hain, phod

Yung Sammy (1st Verse)
Yung Sammy aur Seedhe Maut, dekh bhai gaand toh tutni hai
Bhari rakha poora system, ab life lage meri movie hai
I’m one of a kind aur bitch meri lage mujhe kaafi choosy hai
Ek bandi ho rahi mujhse kaafi frank, mere sar pe chadh ke khud rahi hai
Verse likha maine UK mein, par Delhi mein jaake ye take liya
Kaafi pehle se tha studio mein locked in, fir LA mein jaake ek break liya
Don’t give a fuck about a price tag, mera maan kiya toh phir le liya
Ek beti chod ka faltu bol raha, gaadi ki dikki mein ghar diya
Marta tha bunk mein business classes
But now I fly that shit
Teacher jo kehti thi “tu likhta nahi achha”
She knows I write that shit
Har ek baar mera holy verse
Jaise karta hoon main baptizing
Don’t give a f*** about a b*** ego
Aur karta nahi kabhi main backbiting

YUNG SAMMY & SEEDHE MAUT Verse
Yung Sammy, SM, yaha pe koi rakhna nahi pair, it’s a landmine ting (CALM)
Na chale koi branding, na chale marketing, na chale franchise (ENCORE)
Bata kaise na tutegi gaand ab inki, jab
Bacha koi chaara hi nahi 

YUNG SAMMY
Bata kaise na sukhengi praan, inke baap
Se hai bane koi sayana nahi, bitch 
ENCORE
Mere gang mein cheete hi cheete, aur
Kabhi bhi saapon ko paala hi nahi 
YUNG SAMMY
Likhu jab bhi lage jaise jaan aayi nayi
Beaton pe main chadhun jaise baadh aayi kahin 
CALM
Bags and bags and bags, damn
Khoke se niche toh aata hi nahi
Apno se pada tera paala hi nahi
Gandhi toh tune kabhi chaapa hi nahi
Abey haat 
YUNG SAMMY
Leta hoon main halke mein, tumhe toh bil mein raho
Sher abhi dahda hai nahi
Bhussi bharu chahiye mujhe chaar line hi
Aisa koi bhi din nahi jab ye maal aaye nahi 
CALM
Kholu tera sar jaise taala yahi daala
Tere sar pe main maala, pade thai thai
Galat hue tere haalat yahi
Tera MUDDA banega aaj raat yahi 
ENCORE

en-GB.title: YUNG SAMMY feat. Seedhe Maut - MUDDA (Official Video) [prod. by Wamp]
en-GB.description:
YUNG SAMMY feat. Seedhe Maut - MUDDA (Official Video) [prod. by Wamp]

Listen now: https://DESITRILL.lnk.to/YUNGSAMMY-MUDDA

YUNG SAMMY says “MUDDA” ain’t just a word, it’s an issue, a problem, a whole storm. When me and Seedhe Maut hit the studio, every line we wrote was about the scene, the hustle, the chaos. It’s called “MUDDA” ’cause when YUNG SAMMY and Seedhe Maut jump on a track, it’s not just music, it’s a warning. It’s trouble, it’s ruckus, it’s pressure on the whole game. We went all in, no filter, real talk straight from the hood. Turning struggles into flex, pain into power. “MUDDA” is an anthem, a rager, an energy you can’t ignore. This is heavyweight talk, facts only.”

Lyrics: 
ENCORE VERSE
Seedhe Maut Sammy hai, dikhta bas grey
Chai pe baithe hum London ya Noida
Lulli si shakal ka, bhidenge hum se
Hum rapper complete hai jaise Cu Boi ka
Hona jo waise bhi ho gaya
Tu toh pitega par bol kya karenge tere boy ka
Sona tha bandi ke chucho mein
Lekin vo aaj ki raat se khabar pe soyega
Kha kise kitno ki maa chodi x2
Aah ahh
Kamar se nikala ghoda aur bandi ko
Diya bana ghodi
Aah

Aur baalak aa karte hai muh chodi
Shakle dikhte hain news akhbaaron mein
Jaise main hoon Modi ooh ooh

Calm (1st Verse)
Kaha par hain rapper, ye dikhte nahi, gaayab hain
Dost inke SM pe flip ho rahi
Janwar hain baithe, teen rapper nahi
Papa hu ladko ka, chhaate mein chup ho rahe
Ye mic pe chilla rahe par inke ye jhaate se vocal nahi clip ho rahe, na na
Ye paisa, ye bitches, ye bud hai kamaaya
Bas music se, fatah bin filmon ke
Haan Greater Noida wala shit hai, saath hai Sammy jo
Ek bandi mujhko boli Calm se bajna hai, don’t say no
Main jau jaha paisa jaye, jab launde jaaye jaha booty go
If the truth be told, yaha dono ladke nuke hain, phod

Ek bandi ho rahi mujhse kaafi frank, mere sar pe chadh ke khud rahi hai

Kaafi pehle se tha studio mein locked in, fir LA mein jaake ek break liya
Don’t give a fuck about a price tag, mera maan kiya toh phir le liya
Ek beti chod ka faltu bol raha, gaadi ki dikki mein ghar diya

But now I fly that shit

Lyrics Hindi
अरे सुल्फे के दम मारा गेल्यां भुख्खी खारे सां
हम डिग्गी में दो तेरे शहर के बुक्की ठारें सां
तू पी के घणी भगावै कदे इंस्टा पे लाइव आवैं 
ये राँडया आली हरकत तै मने भौत घणा छौ आवैं सै
ये नकली चैन पहरकै गल में रे तू आन्दा कोनी बल मैं 
ये रोहतक मैं मेरे भाई 1500 की दो आवैं सैं

अरे कदे जेल कदे पहाड़ा मैं या बाजे सेवा लफ़ंडरां की आट मैं कट्टा कट्टे में गोली घलरी 315 की 
अरे ठंडी बियर गेल्यां रे लेग पीस भी लेवां सां
हम माणस मारण की एक जायज़ फ़ीस भी लेवां सां
अरे तेरे बरगें भौत घणे चाण्डे , दिये छोड़ चला कै डांडे , तू माहरें स्कूल मैं पढ़कै हमने ज्ञान सिखावैं  सैं
ये नकली चैन पैर के गल मैं  रे तू आन्दा कोनी बल मैं 
ये रोहतक मैं मेरे भाई 1500 की दो आवैं सैं

रे हमनै  साफ़ साफ़ लिखवा रख्यां सै अपणे गेटां पै
यहाँ गुंडे सुधारे जाते है भाई सस्ते रेटाँ पै 
हम प्रशासन ने रपिया अपने शोक में देवां सां 
ये असले आसले तो मेरे भाई थोक मैं देवां सां
अरे रोहतक में पूछिए नाम ,चण्डीगढ़ ते करा दे काम , अरे म्हारे की डाला खुलकै नै बता कोणसा गावैं सै 
ये नकली चैन पैहरकै गल में रे तू आन्दा कोनी बल मैं 
ये रोहतक मैं मेरे भाई 1500 की दो आवैं सैं

Lyrics English
Arre Sulfe ke dam maara gelya bukhi khare saa
Han diggi mein do tere sehar ke bukki thare sa
Tu pee ke ghani bhagave kade insta pe live aave
Ye randya aali harkat pe Mane bohot Ghana cho aave se
Ye nakli chain pehar ke gal mein re tu anda koni bal mein
Ye Rohtak mein mere bhai 1500 ki do aave se

Arre kade jail kade pahada mein ya baaje se lafandara ki 
Aat mein katta kaate mein goli ghalri 315 ki
Are thandi beer gelya re leg piece bhi leva sa 
Ham Manas maran ki ek jayaj fees bhi leva sa
Arre tere barge bohot ghane chande diye chod chala ke dande
Tu mahre school mein padhke hamne gyan sikhave se
Ye nakli chain pehar ke gal mein re tu anda koni bal mein
Ye Rohtak mein mere bhai 1500 ki do aave se

Re hamne saaf saaf likhwa rakhya se apne geta pe 
Yha gunde sudhare jate hai bhai saste reta pe
Ham parshashan ne rapiya apne shok mein Deva sa
Ye asle asle to mere bhai thik mein Deva sa
Arre rohtak mein puchiye naam Chandigarh te Kara de kaam
Arre mahre ki dhala khulke ne bata konsa gaave se
Ye nakli chain pehar ke gal mein re tu anda koni bal mein
Ye Rohtak mein mere bhai 1500 ki do aave se

➟ Flutes : Naveen Kumar

➟ Assistant mix Engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai

🎬 Video Credits

Maddock Films presents #ParamSundari In cinemas on 29th August 2025

➟ Cast: Sidharth Malhotra and Janhvi Kapoor 
➟ Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
➟ Directed By: Tushar Jalota
➟ Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota & Poonam Shivdasani
➟ Director Of Photography : Santhanakrishnan
➟ Story by: Gaurav Mishra, Aarsh Vora, Tushar Jalota
➟ Screenplay and Dialogues: Aarsh Vora, Tushar Jalota
➟ Music By: Sachin-Jigar
➟ Background Score: Sachin-Jigar
➟ Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya 
➟ Additional Dialogues: Gaurav Mishra
➟ Costume Designer : Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
➟ Director Of Choreography: Brinda Gopal
➟ Publicity Design: Himanshu & Rahul Nanda (H-One)
➟ Lyric Video: Latikesh Sutar

Lyrics:

Pardesiya..
Hai tere pyar mein jab se
Jhankaar si..
Hai dil ke taar mein tab se

Tum ho mere jaanta hun magar
Pohchaauñ tum tak ye kaise khabar

Kab se hun main ummeed meiñ
Hai ankaha jo sun lo agar

Pardesiya..
Mila hai tu mujhe jab se

Maiñ qaid huñ
Tere bhi pyar mein tab se ..

Pardesiya haiñ teri batiyoñ ne 
Kiya pareshan pardesiya..

Pardesiya haiñ teri ankhiyoñ ke
Dil pe nishaan pardesiya..
 
Chhoo ke laboñ se jaise
Jaadu hi kar diya
Saavan ne morni ko
Qaabu mein kar liya

Hum dono ki juda theeñ hastiyaañ
Hoñ kinara bin jaise kashtiyaañ

Aasaan ho aage safar
Tum saath mera chun lo agar

Pardesiya.. 

#SonuNigam #SidharthMalhotra #JanhviKapoor 

© 2025 Universal Music India Pvt. Ltd.

snippet.title: Chhath Ke Tyohar | छठ के त्योहार | Swati Mishra | New Chhath Song 2025 | Bhojpuri Chhath Geet
snippet.description:
👉 Subscribe to Swati Mishra Bhojpuri : https://www.youtube.com/@swatimishrabhojpuri01


 ✨ Chhath Ke Tyohar ✨ — a heart-touching Bhojpuri Chhath Song sung by Swati Mishra, celebrating not just devotion to Chhathi Maiya and Surya Dev, but also the family love, unity, and traditions that make this festival truly special.Lyrics is Penned by Swati Mishra and Story and Concept is Beautifully Written By Rajesh Kumar Mishra.

This song beautifully portrays how Chhath Puja brings families together — from mothers preparing prasad, fathers arranging rituals, to children joining in devotion and joy. It’s an emotional tribute to the roots, respect, and relationships that keep Indian culture alive. ❤️

🎧 Song Credits:
Title: Chhath Ke Tyohar
Singer: Swati Mishra
Lyrics: Swati Mishra
Composer : Saket Suman,Mohit Musik
Music Arranged and Produced by : Mohit Musik
Flute : Prathemesh Salunke
Live Acoustic guitar, Electric guitar and bass : Fahad Qureshi 
Bgm : Mohit Musik
Foley ,Sound Design : Mohit Musik,Saket Suman
Mix & Mastered by : M.M Studio(Mumbai)
Backing Vocals (Chrous): Sejal Keshari,Nishi Dubey,puja Basnet
Label: Swati Mishra Bhojpuri
Language: Bhojpuri


  Video Credits:

Video Director: Manthan Sandhu

Art,Screenplay & script : Manthan Sandhu
Asst Dop : sanjay

💭 Is Saiyaara just a song, or an emotion? Iss video mein aapko milega *Saiyaara ke lyrics ka meaning, story behind the visuals, aur kyu yeh song ban gaya hai **Haridwar se leke social media tak viral*. 

🎬 Full reaction | Lyrics explanation | Emotional connect | Music review — sab kuch ek hi video mein!

👇 Apna opinion comment mein likhna na bhoolna! Aur agar video pasand aaye to Like, Share aur Subscribe zarur karna! 🔔❤

---

🎬 Movie & Music Credits

Director: Mohit Suri (known for Aashiqui 2, Ek Villain)  

Producers: Yash Raj Films, led by Akshaye Vidwani  

Starring (Leads):

Ahaan Panday as Krish Kapoor — debutant from Bollywood’s Panday family, works as a musician in the film  

Aneet Padda as Vaani Batra — debut lead, previously appeared in Salaam Venky, Big Girls Don't Cry, from Amritsar  




---

🎵 Soundtrack & Title Song Details

The Saiyaara soundtrack features seven beautiful tracks released under YRF Music on July 4, 2025  . The title track "Saiyaara" was released June 3, 2025, and is part of this soulful album.

Music Composers:

Main title (“Saiyaara”): Tanishk Bagchi, Faheem Abdullah, Arslan Nizami  

Other contributors: Mithoon, Sachet–Parampara, Rishabh Kant, Vishal Mishra  


Lyricists: Irshad Kamil (title and reprise), Rishabh Kant, Raj Shekhar, Mithoon  

Singers: Title track by Faheem Abdullah; also includes vocalists like Jubin Nautiyal, Shreya Ghoshal, Arijit Singh  



---

🌟 Additional Highlights & Accolades

Saiyaara has smashed box office benchmarks: ₹14.07 Cr by day 1 and over ₹100 Cr in opening weekend — credited to its music and emotional storytelling  

Title track hit Spotify Global Top 50 (#7), first-ever Hindi film song featured  

Industry praise from Ranveer Singh, Mahesh Babu, Kunal Kohli, calling it “scintillating” and a revival of romantic Bollywood music  



---

🎭 Film Plot Overview (No Spoilers)

Ahaan plays Krish Kapoor, a temperamental musician who meets Vaani (Aneet Padda), a journalist and aspiring lyricist  . Their bond—rooted in music and emotion—faces a heartbreaking crisis when Vaani’s early-onset Alzheimer’s creates a dramatic climax, ending on an emotionally charged yet hopeful note  .


---

📝 Summary Table

Role Name

Director Mohit Suri
Producer Yash Raj Films (Akshaye Vidwani)
Lead Hero (Krish) Ahaan Panday
Lead Actress (Vaani) Aneet Padda
Title Music Composers Tanishk Bagchi, Faheem Abdullah, Arslan Nizami
Lyricist (Title Track) Irshad Kamil
Singer (Title Track) Faheem Abdullah



---
